To accept, please click the button below.
</mj-text>
        <mj-button align="left" href="{{.Link}}" background-color="#2563EB">Accept Invite</mj-button>

        <mj-text font-family="Open Sans, Arial" line-height="1.5">
Or Copy this url in the browser: <a href="https://mjml.io/try-it-live/JiyoIAC3N">{{.Link}}</a>
</mj-text>
      <mj-text font-family="Open Sans, Arial">
	- Team Kloudlite
